org.spongepowered.api.registry.util

Annotation Type RegisterCatalog


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE,FIELD})
public @interface RegisterCatalog
    An annotation to mark a Map where it's of type Map<String, CatalogType> such that it is used with a helper to register the static fields of various pseudo enum classes containing "default" CatalogTypes.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      Class<?> value
      The class to register the values to.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String[] ignoredFields
      Gets an array of field names that are to be ignored when mapping fields on the target class.
